version_description: It's neater, in the correct key and is I believe 100% correct
Power chords are used in this one.
Chords given in half-step down tuning as played on the album, without power chords.
This song is in the key of C.

This version is much easier to play on an acoustic guitar and it maintains the original key of the song. The other versions are difficult to play unless you are using all power chords, in which case you would be looking up the Tab, not the Chords.
